845
00:54:50,203 --> 00:54:52,203
Look at you.

846
00:54:54,607 --> 00:54:56,343
Hello.

847
00:54:56,443 --> 00:54:58,443
Hi, hon.

848
00:55:02,449 --> 00:55:05,885
